{"type": "article", "id": 23453, "title": "家用花园铲子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 474100, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115121joCX4dDq2W9pwzSH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组家用花园铲，由日本永塚制作所设计，采用金属加工工艺制成。春天是耕种的季节，他们希望能让人们感受到家庭园艺的乐趣。农铲分成“in、on、above”三个系列色，浅色系代表紫阳花和波斯菊等各种花朵，适合女性和高龄者使用；深色表现土地和蔬菜的颜色；矿物色则指代金银铜。铲子的重量很轻，在 45g 到 220g 之间。售价 900 日元起，<a href=\"http://www.eizuka-ss.com/field-good-%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%82%A2/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151193ljcO42Um5N79MEP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7027027\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115119WbFJALvwh8peBCo0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115120DGn8fVK4UeBiqxCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2027027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115120mvtlyoqbQD3Yg7LS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2027027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}